FNAF Sister Location (Official Release) ►►http://bit.ly/2e5xeOT
FNAF's Baby Attacks Markiplier! ►► http://bit.ly/2dqEqzn

Well it's back to work at my Dayshift at Freddy's. It's only my second day on the job but I think I'm starting to get the hang of it. Don't Yiff, Don't Die, and Kidnap Children. Wait don't kidnap children? - Okay, so maybe I'm a little unsure about that last one, but 2 out of 3 ain't bad. Let's just cover all our options to ensure we see all the endings.
